Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再像以前那样在街上向女孩搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再痛痛快快地打架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 好处总是被你抢跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 孟德那家伙也相当受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我不知道为什么 老是和男人泡在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能指挥进攻南阳的战略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没心情参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说南阳首领孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和作为斗士的你并非生人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是很有缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很笨 但她是个不错的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说孙策和母亲一同寄住在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为南阳斗士的周瑜家中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言说你和孙策母亲的关系也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想攻其不备 连他身边的周瑜一同打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是最适人选
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险起见 我先把话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次南阳战的指挥 是曹操大人的敕命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是孟德下的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是孟德下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不直接跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这种做法本来就与我性格不和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头对拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正的较量才是斗士的根本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操大人现在正躲在地下闭门不出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实传达给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是冰之军师大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使郭嘉死了 表情也毫无变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是孟德的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要用我的做法办事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:01.87,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话　二龙邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你从房顶跳下来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又干这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不能再轻点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩…玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个白痴女儿 竟然说了不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分啊 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个纸门 昨天才刚把纸换好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许昌逐步镇压了关东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校的主力吕蒙却去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈也躲在山里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘宁还在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在南阳的四天王差了三个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成为了曹操的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能保护好伯符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的教训太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因为这个就逃到我房间里来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想小便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿特别疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去啦 公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 大不了在这里解决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨 没纸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不擦就出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿过来 你老老实实地等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 像个小孩似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是打破了纸门就暴怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是周瑜公谨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乌丸族首领
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫蜴顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜴顿?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你们是许昌的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是还礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色不错啊 小霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话真希望都脱光以后再干掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深更半夜的突然跑到人家家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还在人家上厕所的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说都太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么失不失礼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也派吕蒙子明偷袭了成都学园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事再讲得具体些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么晚了还吵吵嚷嚷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆不想受伤的话 还是闪一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴荣 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 你踏到了决不可践踏的地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里异常兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈果然很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说她妈妈这么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还是先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们乌丸族为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许随便行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭一年级的小子想单独攻击君主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早了一百年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于这边的差错给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…别在意了 小{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系都这么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.14,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还可以努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.14,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生从这里开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好久没像这样运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是敌不过年纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操果然还是盯上了南阳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想干突袭这种肮脏的行径
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想堂堂正正地在战斗上决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 你刚刚的态度怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在客人面前打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡的话回自己房间睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 夏侯{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争斗是无法避免的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的伙伴甘宁杀了许昌的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我只是不想用卑鄙的手段复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的到底是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操已经开始攻击南阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预定计划一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然私下见了面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯渊… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是郭嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉死前将你托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被暗杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉拥有能够改变曹操命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变曹操大人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将生命献给了曹操孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会将龙玉弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎 荣耀和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆属于我神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的裁决是真实而正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀了许昌郭嘉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是南阳的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成都正面临危机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 总欠关羽人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没什么好表现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是那样的笨蛋斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦觉醒了 我们就拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次觉醒 玄德都会逐渐为自己的力量所毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要加油保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪里的什么人来 我都不会再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 这里是成都学园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为搞错地方 跑到神社里来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊 校服没看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞 休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是转校生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是哪个学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是以前 我现在也在南阳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是南阳的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张…张飞 你要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从正面堂堂正正地进来 我就夸奖你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来找人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非要打的话 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 张飞又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人不爽的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想张飞要是受伤了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她是伯符?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫伯符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孙策伯符 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不许你碰玄德一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关…关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽…云长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么最近常见到好久不见的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布 你改变了命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和关东的霸王董卓同归于尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出和你相同的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有沉睡在龙玉中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够抑制住三位王体内的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想要让刘备玄德觉醒以尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟连我自身…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只封印了的左眼也产生了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 我像往常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将压制龙的符缝在了纱布里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那只眼睛会散布诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是邪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是符的力量耗尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了将孙策从龙的控制中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是否应该将这个交给孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还在犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎 荣耀和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆属于我神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的裁决是真实而正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有神的仆人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有畏惧神的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同赞美我神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忏悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众 怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟又成熟 且不断朝着美的霸业前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 吴荣的大人魅力怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不会输给那些稚嫩的小女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕对方是初中的古典少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是使用日本刀的高中生美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是幼女谋士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集　一骑当千{\fnSimhei\fs25}Dragon Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士无惨
